"11:106:8" : {s: 11, a: 106, w: 8, r: "زفر", t: "زَفِيرٌۭ", l: "زَفِير", lc: 3, tl: "zafīrun", lb: "দ্বীর্ঘশ্বাস, নিঃশ্বাস, বিলাপ",e: "(is) sighing", b: "আহজারি", i: "menarik nafas", f: 2, rm: "a sigh/sob, draw in breath due to distress, to groan, moan in grief, a sea that makes a roaring, one who carries loads/burdens, calamity/misfortune."},
