"11:107:4" : {s: 11, a: 107, w: 4, r: "دوم", t: "دَامَتِ", l: "دَامُ", lc: 7, tl: "dāmati", lb: "স্থায়ী হওয়া, সর্বদা থাকা",e: "as long as remain", b: "যতদিন থাকবে", i: "selama", f: 2, rm: "To continue, endure, persist, remain, persevere, last, stand still, keep alive."},
